GENERAL_SUBNET=10.1.0.0/16
###              . .1.. -> Client-Gateway
###              . .2.. -> Katran-Gateway
###              . .3.. -> Reals-Gateway
###              . .4.. -> (unused)
###              . .5.. -> Scratch_LB-Gateway
